    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，根节点命名为\"Education_GradeSync\"。这是要画成思维导图的形式吗？还是其他结构？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "root"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，用思维导图。先确定中心主题，后续我们再展开学生端、教师端、数据同步这些分支。目前先把根节点定下来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "root",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把中心节点创建好。根节点显示为\"Education_GradeSync\"，作为整个GradeSync平台的起点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "root",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，我想确认一下显示效果。根节点用的是方括号还是圆括号？教育类系统通常希望看起来正式一些。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "root",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "用的是方括号，显示为圆角矩形，这样既正式又不失亲和力，符合教育产品的调性。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "root",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "完美。那我们先保持这个简洁版本，下周评审会上再展示完整的学生成绩录入、自动同步、家长通知这些子模块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "root",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
